## Next Steps

* New participants are encouraged to download templates from [authors.ietf.org](https://authors.ietf.org) to begin drafting technical ideas.
* Participants interested in introducing new work should monitor the schedule for the IAB New Work Help Desk and relevant Area Dispatch sessions.
* Attendees should monitor the daily morning email updates from Michelle Cotton for daily newcomer highlights and room updates.